"dialogs": [
{
"uid": "D_HERO",
"content": {
"nextID": 7,
"sentence": {
"choice": true,
"sentences": [
{
"id": 1,
"speaker": "O_HERO",
"randomly": true,
"text": {
"en": "It's not a good idea.\r\n\r\nWhat?\r\n\r\nNope.\r\n\r\nI don't understand how I could use these both together.",
"ru": "~041D~0435 ~043B~0443~0447~0448~0430~044F ~0438~0434~0435~044F.\r\n\r\n~0427~0442~043E-~0447~0442~043E?\r\n\r\n~041D~0435~0430.\r\n\r\n~042F ~043D~0438~043A~0430~043A ~043D~0435 ~043C~043E~0433~0443 ~043F~043E~0434~0434~0435~0440~0436~0430~0442~044C ~044D~0442~0443 ~0431~0435~0437 ~0441~043E~043C~043D~0435~043D~0438~044F ~043F~0440~0435~043A~0440~0430~0441~043D~0443~044E ~0437~0430~0442~0435~044E.",
"fr": "Ce n'est pas une bonne idée.\r\n\r\nN'importe quoi !\r\n\r\nNan.\r\n\r\nJe ne vois pas comment je pourrais utiliser ces deux objets ensemble.",
"it": "Non č una buona idea.\r\n\r\nE una cosa qualunque.\r\n\r\nNan.\r\n\r\nNon so come potrei utilizzare questi due oggetti.",
"de": "Das ist keine gute Idee.\r\n\r\nWas?\r\n\r\nNein.\r\n\r\nIch habe keine Ahnung, wie ich das kombinieren soll.",
"tw": "~9019~4E0D~662F~4E00~500B~597D~4E3B~610F\r\n\r\n~4EC0~9EBC~FF1F\r\n\r\n~4E0D~3002\r\n\r\n~6211~4E0D~660E~767D~6211~600E~9EBC~53EF~4EE5~4E00~8D77~4F7F~7528~9019~4E9B~3002",
"ja": "~305D~308C~306F~826F~3044~8003~3048~3067~306F~3042~308A~307E~305B~3093~3002\r\n\r\n~4F55~FF1F\r\n\r\n~3044~3044~3048~3002\r\n\r\n~79C1~306F~3053~308C~3089~3092~3069~306E~3088~3046~306B~4E00~7DD2~306B~4F7F~3046~3053~3068~304C~3067~304D~308B~306E~304B~5206~304B~308A~307E~305B~3093~3002",
