{
"uid": "D_GUARD",
"content": {
"nextID": 25,
"sentence": {
"choice": true,
"sentences": [
{
"id": 9,
"choice": true,
"text": {
"en": "I would ask him for an autograph. Can I go?",
"ru": "~042F ~043C~0435~0447~0442~0430~044E ~0437~0430~043F~043E~043B~0443~0447~0438~0442~044C ~0435~0433~043E ~0430~0432~0442~043E~0433~0440~0430~0444. ~041C~043E~0436~043D~043E ~043F~043E~0434~043E~0439~0442~0438 ~043D~0430 ~043C~0438~043D~0443~0442~043A~0443?",
"fr": "J'aimerais lui demander un autographe. Je peux passer ?",
