{
"id": 1,
"choice": true,
"text": {
"en": "Do you know Botul?",
"ru": "~0410 ~0432~044B ~0445~043E~0440~043E~0448~043E ~0437~043D~0430~0435~0442~0435 ~0411~043E~0442~044E~043B~044F?",
"fr": "Vous connaissez Botul ?",
"it": "Conoscete Botul ?",
"de": "Kennen Sie Botul?",
"tw": "~4F60~77E5~9053Botul~55CE",
"ja": "~3042~306A~305F~306FBotul~3092~77E5~3063~3066~3044~307E~3059~304B~FF1F",
"ko": "~BCF4~D234~C744 ~C544~C2ED~B2C8~AE4C?",
"cn": "~4F60~77E5~9053Botul~5417~FF1F"
},
"sentences": [
{
"id": 12,
"speaker": "O_GUARD",
"text": {
"en": "Only his name.",
"ru": "~042F ~0445~043E~0440~043E~0448~043E ~0437~043D~0430~044E ~0435~0433~043E ~0444~0430~043C~0438~043B~0438~044E.",
"fr": "De nom.",
"it": "Di nome.",
"de": "Nur seinen Namen.",
"tw": "~53EA~6709~4ED6~7684~540D~5B57~3002",
"ja": "~5F7C~306E~540D~524D~3060~3051~3002",
"ko": "~ADF8~C758 ~C774~B984 ~B9CC.",
"cn": "~53EA~6709~4ED6~7684~540D~5B57~3002"
},
"sentences": [
{
"id": 13,
"choice": true,
"text": {
"en": "It seems that this guy is a great philosopher.",
"ru": "~0413~043E~0432~043E~0440~044F~0442, ~043E~043D ~0432~0435~043B~0438~043A~0438~0439 ~0444~0438~043B~043E~0441~043E~0444.",
"fr": "Il parait que c'est un grand philosophe.",
"it": "Pare che sia un grande filosofo.",
"de": "Es scheint, er ist ein großartiger Philosoph.",
"tw": "~4F3C~4E4E~9019~500B~50A2~4F19~662F~4E00~500B~5049~5927~7684~54F2~5B78~5BB6~3002",
"ja": "~3053~306E~7537~306F~5049~5927~306A~54F2~5B66~8005~3060~3068~601D~308F~308C~308B~3002",
"ko": "~C774 ~C0AC~B78C~C740 ~D6CC~B96D~D55C ~CCA0~D559~C790 ~C778 ~AC83 ~AC19~C2B5~B2C8~B2E4.",
"cn": "~770B~6765~8FD9~4E2A~5BB6~4F19~662F~4E00~4F4D~4F1F~5927~7684~54F2~5B66~5BB6~3002"
},
"sentences": [
{
"id": 14,
"speaker": "O_GUARD",
"text": {
"en": "I thought also hear it.",
"ru": "~042F ~0442~043E~0436~0435 ~043E~0431 ~044D~0442~043E~043C ~0441~043B~044B~0448~0430~043B.",
"fr": "J'ai cru aussi entendre ça.",
