{
"id": 3,
"choice": true,
"text": {
"en": "I'd like to order a pie with lots of whipped cream please.",
"ru": "~042F ~0445~043E~0442~0435~043B ~0431~044B ~0437~0430~043A~0430~0437~0430~0442~044C ~043F~0438~0440~043E~0433 ~0441 ~043E~0433~0440~043E~043C~043D~044B~043C ~043A~043E~043B~0438~0447~0435~0441~0442~0432~043E~043C ~0432~0437~0431~0438~0442~044B~0445 ~0441~043B~0438~0432~043E~043A.",
"fr": "Je souhaiterais commander une tarte avec beaucoup de crčme fouettée SVP.",
"it": "Vorrei ordinare una torta con molta crema per favore.",
"de": "Ich würde gerne einen Kuchen mit extra viel Schlagsahne bestellen.",
"tw": "~6211~60F3~8A02~4E00~500B~9921~9905~FF0C~5927~91CF~7684~5976~6CB9~3002",
"ja": "~79C1~306F~305F~304F~3055~3093~306E~30DB~30A4~30C3~30D7~30AF~30EA~30FC~30E0~3067~30D1~30A4~3092~6CE8~6587~3057~305F~3044~3068~601D~3044~307E~3059~3002",
"ko": "~D718~D551 ~D06C~B9BC~C744 ~B9CE~C774 ~BFCC~B824~C11C ~D30C~C774~B97C ~C8FC~BB38~D558~ACE0 ~C2F6~C2B5~B2C8~B2E4.",
"cn": "~6211~60F3~70B9~4E00~4EFD~5E26~6709~5F88~591A~9C9C~5976~6CB9~7684~9985~997C~3002"
},
"sentences": [
{
"id": 8,
"speaker": "O_OPERATOR",
"text": {
"en": "Well sir. Could you give me your credit card number?",
"ru": "~041A~043E~043D~0435~0447~043D~043E. ~041F~0440~043E~0434~0438~043A~0442~0443~0439~0442~0435 ~043D~043E~043C~0435~0440 ~0432~0430~0448~0435~0439 ~043A~0440~0435~0434~0438~0442~043D~043E~0439 ~043A~0430~0440~0442~044B, ~043F~043E~0436~0430~043B~0443~0439~0441~0442~0430.",
"fr": "Trčs bien Monsieur. Pourriez-vous me donner votre numéro de carte de crédit ?",
"it": "Molto bene signore. Potete darmi il numero della vostra carta di credito ?",
"de": "Gerne. Sagen Sie mir bitte Ihre Kreditkartennummer?",
"tw": "~597D~7684~FF0C~5148~751F~3002~4F60~53EF~4EE5~7D66~6211~4F60~7684~4FE1~7528~5361~865F~78BC~55CE~FF1F",
"ja": "~307E~3042~3001~3042~306A~305F~306E~30AF~30EC~30B8~30C3~30C8~30AB~30FC~30C9~756A~53F7~3092~6559~3048~3066~304F~3060~3055~3044~3002",
"ko": "~C54C~ACA0~C2B5~B2C8~B2E4. ~C2E0~C6A9 ~CE74~B4DC ~BC88~D638~B97C ~C54C~B824~C8FC~C2DC~ACA0~C2B5~B2C8~AE4C?",
"cn": "~5148~751F~3002~4F60~80FD~544A~8BC9~6211~4F60~7684~4FE1~7528~5361~53F7~7801~5417~FF1F"
},
"sentences": [
{
"id": 18,
"choice": true,
"never_hide": true,
"text": {
"en": "I lost my credit card.\r\n\r\nCredit card?",
"ru": "~042F ~043F~043E~0442~0435~0440~044F~043B ~0441~0432~043E~044E ~043A~0440~0435~0434~0438~0442~043A~0443.\r\n\r\n~041A~0440~0435~0434~0438~0442~043D~043E~0439 ~043A~0430~0440~0442~044B?",
"fr": "J'ai paumé ma carte de crédit.\r\n\r\nCarte de crédit ?",
"it": "Ho perduto la mia carta di credito.\r\n\r\nCarta di credito ?",
"de": "Ich habe meine Kreditkarte verloren.\r\n\r\nKreditkarte?",
"tw": "~6211~5931~53BB~4E86~4FE1~7528~5361~3002\r\n\r\n~4FE1~7528~5361~FF1F",
"ja": "~79C1~306F~30AF~30EC~30B8~30C3~30C8~30AB~30FC~30C9~3092~7D1B~5931~3057~305F~3002\r\n\r\n~30AF~30EC~30B8~30C3~30C8~30AB~30FC~30C9~FF1F",
"ko": "~B098~B294 ~C2E0~C6A9 ~CE74~B4DC~B97C ~C783~C5B4 ~BC84~B838~B2E4.\r\n\r\n~C2E0~C6A9 ~CE74~B4DC?",
"cn": "~6211~4E22~5931~4E86~4FE1~7528~5361~3002\r\n\r\n~4FE1~7528~5361~FF1F"
},
"sentences": [
{
"id": 20,
"speaker": "O_OPERATOR",
"text": {
"en": "I can not process your order without payment.",
"ru": "~042F ~043D~0435 ~043C~043E~0433~0443 ~043F~0440~0438~043D~044F~0442~044C ~0432~0430~0448 ~0437~0430~043A~0430~0437 ~0431~0435~0437 ~043E~043F~043B~0430~0442~044B.",
"fr": "Je ne peux pas traiter votre commande sans paiement.",
"it": "Non posso procedere all'ordine senza pagamento.",
