"dir": "FRONT",
"keep_dir": true,
"text": {
"en": "I put everything and anything in this drawer.\r\nThis is very useful to find something.",
"ru": "~0412 ~044D~0442~043E~043C ~044F~0449~0438~043A~0435 ~043B~0435~0436~0438~0442 ~0432~0441~0435, ~0447~0442~043E ~0443 ~043C~0435~043D~044F ~043A~043E~0433~0434~0430-~043B~0438~0431~043E ~0431~044B~043B~043E.\r\n~041B~0443~0447~0448~0435~0435 ~043C~0435~0441~0442~043E ~0434~043B~044F ~0442~043E~0433~043E, ~0447~0442~043E~0431~044B ~0447~0442~043E-~043D~0438~0431~0443~0434~044C ~043D~0430~0439~0442~0438.",
"fr": "Je range tout et n'importe quoi dans ce tiroir.\r\nC'est trčs pratique pour retrouver un truc. C'est forcément dedans.",
"it": "Metto tutto in questo tiretto.\r\nE molto pratico per ritrovare une coas. Deve essere dentro.",
